results.title: Terry de Havilland, Cobbler to the Stars, Is Dead at 81
results.abstract: He made python boots for Nureyev, black leather thigh-high boots for Jacqueline Onassis and platforms for Kate Moss that spelled out a vulgarity in crystals.
